column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY DAIRY MILK CHOCOLATE EGG MILK WITH DAIM PIECES 86.000 GR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210179555
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, cocoa butter, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa mass, emulsifiers (E442, E476, SOYA lecithin, sunflower lecithin), blanched ALMONDS, sweetened condensed skimmed MILK, salt, flavourings, dried skimmed MILK, dried whey (from MILK), MILK fat, reduced protein whey (from MILK). NOT SUITABLE FOR VEGETARIANS **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolate. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.COCOA SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN OTHER NUTS. Date available: 03/27/2018 Date last updated by company: 03/27/2018
